Dialogue: 3,0:00:19.29,0:00:29.60,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}mas meus sonhos e {\c&H0000C2&}esperanças {\c&HFFFFFF&}que vêm e vão permanecem intactos
Dialogue: 3,0:00:29.60,0:00:34.18,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Eu desejo do fundo do meu {\c&H0000C2&}coração {\c&HFFFFFF&}que eles se realizem
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.56,0:00:38.94,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}toda vez que {\c&H0000C2&}mergulho {\c&HFFFFFF&}na escuridão
Dialogue: 3,0:00:38.94,0:00:43.73,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Temos a impressão de que estamos {\c&H0000C2&}seguindo {\c&HFFFFFF&}em frente
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.73,0:00:49.82,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}porque não {\c&H0000C2&}queremos {\c&HFFFFFF&}ceder ao nosso desespero
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.82,0:00:56.91,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ainda que nossas {\c&H0000C2&}preces {\c&HFFFFFF&}desapareçam entre as sombras,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.91,0:01:01.38,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}nós vamos fazê-las {\c&H0000C2&}brilhar {\c&HFFFFFF&}mais forte outra vez
Dialogue: 3,0:01:01.38,0:01:09.22,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Seguindo {\c&H0000C2&}apenas {\c&HFFFFFF&}o que nos inspirou,
Dialogue: 3,0:01:09.22,0:01:16.03,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}nós procuramos pelas {\c&H0000C2&}nossas {\c&HFFFFFF&}razões de viver
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.74,0:01:21.45,OP BR,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Nós {\c&H0000C2&}procuramos...
